From 223692784e74cc735ad63333f56168dc6414ff8d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Salman Wahib <sxlmnwb.dev@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 2026 23:37:39 +0700
Subject: [PATCH] sched: add BORE Scheduler v6.6.3 for
 android_kernel_google_msm-4.14

Burst-Oriented Response Enhancer (BORE) scheduler improves interactivity
by tracking burst behavior per-task and adjusting vruntime penalties accordingly.

Source: https://github.com/sxlmnwb/bore-scheduler-android
Patch: 0001-android_kernel_google_msm-4.14-bore-6.6.3.patch

Tested Kernel Source: https://github.com/LineageOS/android_kernel_google_msm-4.14
Branch: lineage-23.2

Tested-by: Salman Wahib <sxlmnwb.dev@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: Masahito S <firelzrd@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Salman Wahib <sxlmnwb.dev@gmail.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/floral_defconfig |   4 +
 include/linux/sched.h               |  35 +++
 include/linux/sched/bore.h          |  40 +++
 init/Kconfig                        |  17 ++
 kernel/Kconfig.hz                   |  17 ++
 kernel/fork.c                       |   9 +
 kernel/futex.c                      |  15 +-
 kernel/sched/Makefile               |   1 +
 kernel/sched/bore.c                 | 453 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 kernel/sched/core.c                 |  19 +-
 kernel/sched/debug.c                |   6 +
 kernel/sched/fair.c                 |  64 +++-
 kernel/sched/sched.h                |   5 +
 13 files changed, 680 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 include/linux/sched/bore.h
